title: >>> "The PIERCER" vs. "Quick SAND"
body_text:
It's time for the "Ultimate Poster Contest"!
Justin Pierce, winner of the DODGEBALL 17 contest, goes head-to-head with DODGEBALL TWENTY-SIX contest winner, Dan Spengeman.
This is a battle of two men that have changed the course of dodgeball history forever. Good luck to both competitors.
